+## 🔭 Tomorrow's Preview — Day 5
+
+We have *labels*. Tomorrow we want *insights*. The boss doesn't only want to know "35% negative" — she wants to know **WHY** they're negative. Is it the delivery? The pricing? The build quality?
+
+On Day 5 we'll add:
+- **Aspect-based analysis** (e.g. *Delivery: Negative, Quality: Positive*)
+- **Top keyword extraction** across all reviews
+- An **overall product score** (X out of 10)
+- Auto-translation for non-English reviews
